## 4. Absolute Ethical Restrictions (سياسة الاستخدام الأخلاقي)
By cloning, copying, modifying, deploying, or utilizing this software in any capacity, you explicitly agree to the following legally and morally binding restrictions. You SHALL NOT use or deploy this software for:
1.  Any platform, organization, or entity that promotes atheism, actively undermines Islamic values, or attacks scholarly religious institutions.
2.  Hostile military/intelligence entities, or entities that promote sectarian hatred, violence, or unlawful discrimination.
3.  The distribution, streaming, or hosting of unethical, immoral, or explicit media/content.

## 5. Termination
Any use, deployment, or redistribution of this software that violates the Ethical Restrictions listed in Section 4 automatically and immediately voids this license. Upon termination, your right to use, host, or distribute the codebase is permanently revoked, and any active deployments must be dismantled.

